com.here.android.mpa.ar

Class ARController.UpViewTransitionParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.ar.ARController.UpViewTransitionParams
  • Enclosing class:
    ARController

    public final class ARController.UpViewTransitionParams
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates parameters which affect the Up view transition. The Up view transition is the action that occurs when transitioning from the Down view to the Up view.
